name: breast_cancer
title: Breast Cancer - Wisconsin
description: Dataset for breast tumor diagnosis. Predict diagnosis: B = benign, M = malignant. Features are computed from a digitized image of a fine needle aspirate (FNA) of a breast mass. They describe characteristics of the cell nuclei present in the image.
id_description: A unique identifier for each sample in the dataset.
target_description: A binary variable indicating the diagnosis of the breast tissue (M = malignant, B = benign).

name: coupon_recommendations
title: In-vehicle coupon recommendation
description: This data studies whether a person will accept the coupon recommended to them in different driving scenarios.
target_description: Binary variable indicating responding will accept the coupon recommendation (1) or not (0)

name: credit_approval
title: Credit Approval
description: This dataset concerns credit card applications.  All attribute names and values have been changed to meaningless symbols to protect confidentiality of the data.

name: electrical_grid
title: Electrical Grid Stability Simulated Data Data Set
description: The local stability analysis of the 4-node star system (electricity producer is in the center) implementing Decentral Smart Grid Control concept.
target_description: the stability label of the system : stable or unstable

name: employee_attrition
title: Employee Attrition dataset from PyCaret
description: "The task is to predict whether an employee underwent attrition using predictor features such as satisfaction_level, salary category, department, average monthly hours, promotion in last 5 years, etc."
target_description: Binary variable indicating attrition (1) or no attrition (0)

name: image_segmentation
title: Image Segmentation
description: Image data described by high-level numeric-valued attributes; Original contained 7 classes. The multi-class target feature is converted to a two-class nominal target feature by re-labeling the majority class as positive (P) and all others as negative (N).

name: mushroom
title: Mushroom Data Set
description: From Audobon Society Field Guide; mushrooms described in terms of physical characteristics; classification: poisonous or edible.
target_description: Classification of mushrooms - poisonous (p) or edible (e )

name: nba
title: NBA binary classification dataset from Pycaret
description: NBA binary classification dataset from Pycaret.
target_description: Classification of player: play in nba for 5 years+ (1) or not (0)

name: online_shopping
title: Online Shoppers Purchasing Intention
description: Dataset for real-time prediction of online shoppers purchasing intention.
target_description: Binary variable indicating visitor session ending in shopping (1) or not (0)

name: spambase
title: Spambase Data Set
description: Classifying Email as Spam or Non-Spam.

name: telco_churn
title: Telco customer churn
description: A fictional telco company's customer churn based on a variety of possible factors. The churn column indicates whether or not the customer left within the last month.
target_description: Whether customer churned within the last month (Yes) or not (No)

name: titanic
title: Titanic Passenger Survival dataset
description: The well-known Titanic dataset used to develop models to predict if a passenger survived the shipwreck.
target_description: A binary variable indicating whether or not the passenger survived (0 = No, 1 = Yes).
